n-menu-item-2" href="/loi/radiographics" tabindex="" class="nav-link text-small-bold">All Issues</a></li><li class="nav-item pr-xl-24"><div class="dropdown"><a id="publication-menu-item-3" href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-small-bold">Collections</a><div aria-labelledby="publication-menu-item-3" class="dropdown-menu"><a href="/page/radiographics/specialissues" class="dropdown-item">Monograph</a><a href="/topic/article-types/arttype-cookyjar?sortBy=Earliest" class="dropdown-item">Cases from the Cooky Jar</a><a href="/page/radiographics/visual-abstract" class="dropdown-item">Visual Abstracts</a><a href="/page/podcasts#radiographics" class="dropdown-item">Podcasts</a></div></div></li><li class="nav-item pr-xl-24"><div class="dropdown"><a id="publication-menu-item-4" href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-small-bold">Authors/Reviewers</a><div aria-labelledby="publication-menu-item-4" class="dropdown-menu"><a href="/page/radiographics/rgauthor_instructions" class="dropdown-item">Instructions for Authors </a><a href="https://mc.manuscriptcentral.com/rg" class="dropdown-item">Submit a Manuscript </a><a href="/page/authorservices" class="dropdown-item">Author Services</a><a href="/page/radiographics/peer-review" class="dropdown-item">For Reviewers</a></div></div></li><li class="nav-item pr-xl-24"><div class="dropdown"><a id="publication-menu-item-5" href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-small-bold">Core Learning</a><div aria-labelledby="publication-menu-item-5" class="dropdown-menu"><a href="/page/radiographics/rgteam/top10Home" class="dropdown-item">Top 10 Reading List</a><a href="/page/radiographics/abr-core-exam-study-guide" class="dropdown-item">ABR Core Exam Blueprints Article Index</a><a href="/page/radiog